response:
The article 16 of the Organic Law n° 2020-003 of 24/01/2020 (1) give the The Mediator of the Republic the right to keep up to date information and publishes at least once a year, in the Official Journal of the Republic of Togo, the list of names, the nature of functions, goods and assets of public officials.

Sources: 
(1) The article 8 of the Organic Law n° 2020-003 of 24/01/2020 (1), requires that the declarant indicates the following general elements: 

- his full civil status, his Togolese nationality and / or his
other nationalities where applicable, his professional address, his home address, his matrimonial statuts and the functions performed;
- the civil status of the related person (s), their nationality Togolese and / or other nationalities where applicable, with their address and professional situation;
- his gross annual income related to the mandate or function occupied, as well as its income from all other sources in Togo or abroad;
- the gross annual income of his spouse from all sources in Togo or abroad.


Sources:
(1) https://jo.gouv.tg/sites/default/files/JO/JOS_29_01_2020%20-65E%20ANNEE%20N%C2%B0%2003%20TER.pdf#page=2

